de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.ontmatching.yetanotheralignmentapi

Class Correspondence

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.ontmatching.yetanotheralignmentapi.Correspondence

  • public class Correspondence
extends Object
    A Correspondence contains a relation that holds between two elements from two different ontologies. This is also known as "Mapping Cell" or "Cell".
    Author:
    Sven Hertling, Jan Portisch
